        PdfData class org.jpedal.objects.PdfData Holds text data for extraction and manipulation. Pdf routines create 'raw' text data. Grouping routines will attempt to intelligently stitch together the 'raw' data and leave it as 'processed data' in this class. We recommend you access JPedal using only public methods listed in API.
